 Q.  The 16th hole, No. 7, where you hit your ball to the left?  
PÃDRAIG HARRINGTON: I was sure I was going to make a birdie.  I hit a super third shot and a super putt.  I couldn't believe I hung it to the left of the hole.  They always turn your way.   
