 Q.  Do you think we're looking at a score of 20-plus-under this weekend?  
PÃDRAIG HARRINGTON: All depends on the weather.  The conditions are great out there.  You know, the golf course is presented in great condition and when you present the golf course in good condition, guys will hole putts.  There's no defending a golf course when you have it in good condition and the weather is good.   
